{"post_stream":{"posts":[{"id":3158557,"name":"Marcos Hervis","username":"Marcos","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/9de0a6/{size}.png","created_at":"2023-03-06T19:16:06.125Z","cooked":"

We (3653) recently won South Florida Regional as a 2nd pick for the first alliance. For most of us this is our last year on the team and we want to build the best robot possible for our first time and last at worlds.

We are currently pretty set on building a swerve robot for worlds. We have experimented in the past with swerve but never fully committed on it. It is pretty late but all of us are truly committed to this but a lot of the parts are currently out of stock.

If any team has any Neos, falcons, or any spare swerve modules. Please contact us and we can pay full price.
